Quality Management Officer - PT Aero Systems Indonesia
Quality Management Officer  -
Quality Management Officer
Responsibilities
Analyzes and modifies quality standards that compliance with industry and corporate specifications.Translates business requirements into workable process and procedure.Conducts audit on production work process and procedures to achieve quality goals.Tests parts/complete products, returns rejects for repair or disposal, and ensures that company and product quality requirements are met. Recommends repair procedures, and analyses results and findings of all inspection activity.Monitors the record of defects and failure rates.Documents the company’s quality policy and procedures to ensure compliance with legal corporate specifications.Maintain efficient filling and documentation system of all quality  related data, file and documents. Job Requirement Male, maximum 30 years oldMinimum Bachelor Degree any major with minimum 3 years working experience in Quality field from any industry .Familiar with ISO 9001:2008 requirements.Have ability to work independently and in team.Fluent in English, both oral and written.
